    "pagination_interaction": "IncludeLocationIds prepend runs AFTER ApplySort and ApplyPaging. Missing locations are inserted at index 0 of the already-paged result.Results list. This means: (a) the confirmed location appears ONLY at items[0] of whichever page was requested — NOT duplicated across pages; (b) totalCount is NOT incremented for the prepended item; (c) first:1 with a confirmed location returns [confirmedLocation] only, even if that location is naturally on page 3."
